bers%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20into%20all%20the%20allegations%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20being%20investigated%20from%20all%20angles%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20PTI%20Videos%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Subhash's%20brother%20Bikas%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20my%20brother%20to%20get%20justice.%20I%20want%20this%20country%20to%20have%20a%20legal%20process%20through%20which%20even%20men%20can%20get%20justice.%20I%20want%20strict%20action%20against%20those%20sitting%20on%20a%20legal%20chair%20and%20doing%20corruption%20because%20if%20this%20continues%2C%20how%20will%20people%20expect%20justice.%26quot%3B%20Alleging%20corruption%20in%20the%20system%2C%20he%20said%20justice%20could%20only%20be%20expected%20when%20it%20is%20corruption-free.%20When%20every%20party%20is%20heard%20equally%20and%20arguments%20are%20done%20based%20on%20facts%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B....can%20expect%20justice%20only%20when%20decisions%20are%20made%20based%20of%20facts%20and%20if%20it%20does%20not%20happen%2C%20then%20people%20will%20slowly%20start%20losing%20faith%20in%20the%20judicial%20system.%20It%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20people%20may%20get%20afraid%20to%20get%20married.%20Men%20may%20start%20feeling%20that%20if%20they%20get%20married%2C%20they%20will%20just%20end%20up%20being%20an%20ATM%20for%20vending%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash's%20body%20was%20found%20hanging%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20the%20Manjunath%20Layout%20area%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20the%20Marathahalli%20police%20station%20limits%2C%20on%20Monday.%20A%20placard%20reading%20%26quot%3BJustice%20is%20due%26quot%3B%20was%20found%20in%20the%20room%20where%20he%20allegedly%20ended%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20the%20extreme%20step%2C%20he%20recorded%20an%20over%2080-minute%20video%20on%20Rumble%2C%20explaining%20the%20circumstances%20behind%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20Subhash%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20that%20I%20should%20kill%20myself%20because%20the%20money%20I%20earn%20is%20making%20my%20enemies%20stronger.%20That%20same%20money%20will%20be%20used%20to%20destroy%20me%2C%20and%20this%20cycle%20will%20keep%20going.%26quot%3B%20Subhash's%20uncle%20Pawan%20Kumar%20alleged%20his%20nephew%20was%20being%20harassed%20and%20tortured%20for%20money%20and%20that%20he%20was%20also%20humiliated%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20He%20was%20losing%20the%20case%20(filed%20by%20his%20wife).%20He%20was%20being%20tortured.%20They%20(wife%20and%20family)%20were%20constantly%20demanding%20money%20from%20him.%20To%20the%20best%20of%20his%20capacity%2C%20he%20was%20giving%20her%20money%20for%20child%20maintenance%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20uncle%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20family%20demanded%20Rs%2040%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20doubled%20it%20later%2C%20and%20then%20wanted%20Subhash%20to%20provide%20Rs%201%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20also%20charged%20that%20Subhash's%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20was%20'minting'%20money%20from%20his%20nephew%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20child%20maintenance%2C%20for%20the%20couple's%20four-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wondered%20how%20much%20money%20would%20be%20required%20to%20raise%20a%20child%20of%20this%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20wife%20even%20said%20that%20he%20should%20commit%20suicide%20if%20he%20cannot%20pay%20the%20amount%20to%20which%20the%20judge%20also%20laughed.%20This%20really%20hurt%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20said%20the%20family%20had%20no%20idea%20Subhash%20may%20do%20something%20like%20this.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20made%20a%20time-table%20for%20everything.%26quot%3B%20Subhash's%20cousin%2C%20Bajrang%20Agarwal%20alleged%20that%20the%20victim's%20wife%20and%20family%20were%20constantly%20demanding%20money%20from%20him.%20Till%20the%20time%20he%20was%20giving%20money%2C%20things%20were%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20stopped%20paying%20exorbitant%20amounts%20as%20per%20their%20demands%2C%20the%20dispute%20started%20again%20and%20she%20started%20living%20separately%20with%20the%20child.%20A%20divorce%20case%20was%20going%20on.%20They%20filed%20so%20many%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20that%20he%20broke%20down%20and%20he%20ended%20his%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20videos%20in%20Samastipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20demanded%20that%20those%20who%20had%20harassed%20Subhash%20should%20be%20punished%20so%20that%20he%20coulf%20get%20justice%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bsoul%20could%20rest%20in%20peace.%26quot%3B%20Meanwhile%2C%20Nikita's%20uncle%2C%20Sushil%20Kumar%20claimed%20himself%20innocent%20and%20said%20that%20neither%20he%20nor%20any%20member%20of%20his%20family%20was%20present%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20know%20that%20I%20am%20also%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%20I%20am%20innocent.%20I%20wasn't%20even%20there.%20We%20got%20to%20know%20about%20his%20suicide%20through%20the%20media.%20None%20of%20our%20family%20members%20were%20present%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20incident.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20case%20going%20on%20in%20the%20court%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years%20and%20in%20this%20duration%2C%20we%20have%20had%20no%20communication%20with%20him%20or%20his%20family.%20We%20are%20not%20at%20fault.%20Case%20is%20going%20on...%20Court%20will%20decide%20and%20give%20the%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI%20Videos%20in%20Jaunpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20Subhash%20are%20false%20and%20Nikita%20will%20soon%20answer%20to%20all%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20prelim