tive%2C%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20donations%20have%20poured%20into%20an%20online%20fundraiser%20for%20his%20legal%20defense%2C%20with%20messages%20supporting%20him%20and%20even%20celebrating%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%2C%20%26quot%3BWanted%26quot%3B%20posters%20with%20the%20faces%20of%20CEOs%20have%20appeared%20on%20walls.%20Websites%20are%20selling%20Mangione%20merchandise%2C%20including%20hats%20with%20%26quot%3BCEO%20Hunter%26quot%3B%20printed%20across%20a%20bullseye.%20And%20some%20social%20media%20users%20have%20swooned%20over%20his%20smile%20and%20six-pack%20abs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20murder%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20a%20father%20of%20two%2C%20in%20a%20brazen%20shooting%20on%20Dec.%204%20outside%20a%20Manhattan%20hotel%20before%20an%20industry%20conference%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20five-day%20manhunt%20for%20the%20masked%20assailant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crime%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20has%20been%20broadly%20condemned%2C%20but%20the%20Ivy%20League%20educated%2C%20photogenic%2026-year-old%20has%20become%20an%20unsettling%20mixture%20of%20folk%20hero%2C%20celebrity%2C%20and%20online%20crush%20in%20certain%20circles.%20His%20support%20has%20only%20seemingly%20intensified%20since%20his%20arrest%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20messages%20on%20the%20crowd-sourced%20fundraising%20site%20GiveSendGo%20reflect%20a%20deep%20frustration%20shared%20by%20many%20Americans%20over%20the%20U.S.%20healthcare%20system%20-%20where%20some%20treatments%20and%20reimbursements%20can%20be%20denied%20to%20patients%20depending%20on%20their%20insurance%20coverage%20-%20as%20well%20as%20broader%20anger%20over%20rising%20income%20inequality%20and%20soaring%20executive%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDenying%20healthcare%20coverage%20to%20people%20is%20murder%2C%20but%20no%20one%20gets%20charged%20with%20that%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20donor%20wrote%2C%20calling%20the%20killing%20a%20%26quot%3Bjustifiable%20homicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20others%20simply%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BDeny%2C%20Defend%2C%20Depose%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20words%20reportedly%20written%20on%20the%20shell%20casings%20found%20at%20the%20murder%20scene%20and%20intended%20to%20invoke%20tactics%20some%20accuse%20insurers%20of%20using%20to%20avoid%20paying%20out%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20%2431%2C000%20had%20been%20raised%20as%20of%20Wednesday%20on%20GiveSendGo%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFelipe%20Rodriguez%2C%20a%20former%20NYPD%20detective%20sergeant%2C%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20made%20him%20a%20martyr%20for%20all%20the%20troubles%20people%20have%20had%20with%20their%20own%20insurance%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodriguez%2C%20now%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20the%20John%20Jay%20College%20of%20Criminal%20Justice%20in%20New%20York.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20who%20hasn't%20had%20run-ins%20with%20their%20insurance%3F%20But%20he's%20a%20stone-cold%20killer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20is%20being%20held%20in%20Pennsylvania%20on%20gun%20and%20forgery%20charges%20while%20prosecutors%20in%20New%20York%20seek%20his%20extradition.%20His%20lawyer%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20plead%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20Pennsylvania%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrustration%20And%20Anger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20New%20York%20City%20Police%20Commissioner%20Jessica%20Tisch%20said%20police%20have%20matched%20a%20gun%20found%20on%20Mangione%20with%20the%20shell%20casings%20recovered%20at%20the%20scene%20and%20his%20fingerprints%20with%20a%20water%20bottle%20and%20energy%20bar%20wrapper%20found%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20evidence%20includes%20handwritten%20documents%20found%20in%20his%20possession%20casting%20his%20alleged%20crime%20as%20a%20legitimate%20response%20to%20what%20he%20viewed%20as%20corporate%20greed%2C%20some%20media%20outlets%20have%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20lashed%20out%20himself%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20he%20was%20led%20into%20a%20courthouse%2C%20shouting%20in%20part%2C%20%26quot%3B...completely%20out%20of%20touch%20and%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20intelligence%20of%20the%20American%20people!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmericans%20pay%20more%20for%20health%20care%20than%20residents%20of%20any%20other%20country%2C%20and%20data%20shows%20spending%20on%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20out-of-pocket%20costs%2C%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20hospital%20services%20has%20all%20increased%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20insurers%20like%20UnitedHealth%20most%20often%20manage%20health%20benefits%20on%20behalf%20of%20employers%20and%20the%20government%2C%20which%20have%20a%20say%20in%20what%20services%20and%20drugs%20are%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20suffered%20from%20chronic%20back%20pain%20that%20impacted%20his%20daily%20life%2C%20according%20to%20friends%20and%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20though%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20his%20personal%20health%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20underestimate%20the%20anger%20and%20angst%20people%20have%20with%20their%20insurance%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Shapiro%2C%20a%20former%20FBI%20agent%20and%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20John%20Jay%20College%20of%20Criminal%20Justice%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShapiro%20said%20he%20had%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20the%20reaction%20to%20Mangione%2C%20but%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20so%20farfetched%20given%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20ease%20of%20cheering%20this%20anonymously%20on%20the%20Internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20TikTok%2C%20users%20shared%20videos%20and%20photos%20of%20Mangione's%20outburst%20with%20messages%20of%20praise%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bthis%20man%20is%20an%20absolute%20legend%26