icide%20reportedly%20after%20he%20was%20falsely%20implicated%20in%20rape%20and%20dowry%20cases%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20written%20complaint%20addressed%20to%20then%20Sarita%20Vihar%20Police%20Station%20in-charge%20and%20a%20suicide%20note%20purportedly%20written%20by%20Arvind%20Bharti%20claimed%20his%20wife%2C%20Richa%2C%20wrongly%20accused%20him%20and%20his%20family%20of%20various%20acts%2C%20and%20harassed%20them%20with%20false%20cases%20even%20after%20their%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Bharti%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Yamuna%20Vihar%2C%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bblackmailed%20and%20tortured%20day%20and%20night%26quot%3B%20by%20Richa%2C%20and%20that%20she%20was%20solely%20responsible%20for%20his%20death.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20had%20little%20hope%20from%20the%20police%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20seen%20copies%20of%20the%20written%20police%20complaint%20and%20the%20purported%20suicide%20note%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20written%20in%20Hindi.%20While%20the%20complaint%20letter%20was%20written%20a%20day%20before%20Bharti's%20death%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20when%20it%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20physiotherapist%20before%20he%20joined%20a%20computer%20firm%2C%20died%20by%20suicide%20on%20December%2015%2C%202017.%20Richa%20was%20arrested%20following%20his%20death%20and%20later%20granted%20bail.%20The%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComplaint%20Letter%20To%20Police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20six-page%20letter%20to%20Sarita%20Vihar%20Police%2C%20Bharti%20explained%20how%20his%20wife%20pushed%20him%20to%20take%20the%20extreme%20step.%20He%20said%20he%20and%20Richa%20had%20a%20love%20marriage%20in%202008%20but%20her%20behaviour%20towards%20him%20and%20his%20family%20changed%20drastically%20after%20that%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20used%20to%20register%20false%20police%20complaints%2C%20due%20to%20which%20we%20stayed%20together%20only%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20She%20later%20filed%20a%20false%20dowry%20case%20against%20me.%20I%20was%20discharged%20in%20the%20case%20by%20a%20Delhi%20court%20in%202013%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharti%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20couple%20eventually%20parted%20ways%20in%202016%20but%20the%20alleged%20harassment%20still%20did%20not%20stop.%20Richa%20often%20followed%20Bharti%20to%20his%20office%20and%20his%20coaching%20institute%20to%20insult%20him%20and%20her%20actions%20also%20cost%20him%20his%20job%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20also%20alleged%20that%20his%20former%20wife%20once%20lodged%20a%20false%20case%20of%20rape%20against%20him.%20%26quot%3BThe%20police%20physically%20and%20mentally%20tortured%20me%20and%20refused%20to%20register%20my%20complaint%20(against%20her).%20A%20compromise%20was%20reached%20and%20they%20sent%20me%20to%20Richa's%20house%20where%20her%20family%20stripped%20me%20and%20locked%20me%20in%20a%20room.%20I%20was%20neither%20given%20any%20water%20to%20drink%20nor%20food%20to%20eat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20said%20Richa%20filed%20a%20fresh%20rape%20case%20against%20him%20when%20his%20brother%2C%20Vipin%2C%20arrived%20with%20the%20police%20to%20rescue%20him%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20alleged%20Richa%20often%20pressured%20him%20with%20her%20demands%20for%20money.%20%26quot%3B...%20I%20cannot%20even%20complain%20to%20anyone%20because%20I%20know%20that%20another%20false%20case%20will%20be%20filed%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20on%20one%20occasion%2C%20Richa%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20to%20me.%20Even%20the%20police%20and%20the%20Human%20Rights%20(Commission)%20have%20not%20accepted%20your%20and%20your%20father's%20complaint%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Faith%20In%20Police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20alleged%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20Richa%20to%20blackmail%20and%20threaten%20him%20since%20her%20false%20complaints%20were%20always%20registered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%2C%20on%20one%20occasion%2C%20Richa%20forcibly%20took%20away%20his%20bag%20with%20his%20office%20laptop%2C%20wallet%2C%20his%20bike%20documents%2C%20money%20and%20a%20company's%20invoice%20with%20a%20cheque%20of%20Rs%2032%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20listening%20to%20Richa%20for%20one%20last%20time%20and%20killing%20myself.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20shall%20die%20this%20way%20everyday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuicide%20Note%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20four-page%20note%2C%20Bharti%20said%20he%20was%20writing%20his%20%26quot%3Blast%20letter%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20his%20family%20to%20not%20mourn%20his%20death.%20He%20provided%20details%20of%20the%20items%20that%20were%20reportedly%20forcibly%20taken%20away%20by%20Richa%2C%20and%20of%20money%20that%20he%20owed%20to%20some%20of%20his%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20urged%20his%20family%20to%20move%20on%20with%20their%20lives.%20%26quot%3BGod%20will%20punish%20her%20(Richa)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20suffer%20day%20and%20night%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20have%20to%20take%20this%20extreme%20step%20one%20day%20or%20the%20other...%20I%20am%20very%20tired%20and%20I%20cannot%20suffer%20for%20another%20second.%20Please%20do%20not%20take%20action%20against%20Richa...%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20alive%20and%20your%20life%20might%20also%20get%20spoiled.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Miss%20Him%20Even%20Today'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind's%20mother%20said%20she%20misses%20her%20son.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20hang%20Arvind's%20photo%20on%20the%20wall%20because%20I%20miss%20him%20even%20today.%20His%20former%20wife%20was