el-stream-online%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Google's%20quantum%20computing%20breakthrough%20is%20such%20a%20big%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222496%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google's%20Willow%20chip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6758712fdc8b666017f24d3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221872%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20announced%20a%20new%20quantum%20computing%20milestone%20with%20its%20Willow%20chip.%3Cp%3EGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20unveiled%20its%20Willow%20chip%20this%20week%2C%20marking%20a%20milestone%20in%20the%20quantum%20computing%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20quantum%20researcher%20compared%20Google's%20advancement%20to%20mobile%20networks%20jumping%20from%201G%20to%202G.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20news%20represents%20a%20breakthrough%2C%20real-world%20applications%20are%20likely%20still%20years%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-unveiled-quantum-computer-chip-willow-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20new%20Willow%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20not%20show%20up%20in%20consumer%20products%20in%20the%20near%20future%20%E2%80%94%20however%2C%20quantum%20computing%20researchers%20say%20it%20represents%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20chip%20solves%20a%20challenge%20that's%20existed%20in%20quantum%20computing%20for%20nearly%2030%20years%2C%20Google%20said%20in%20its%20announcement%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20is%20reducing%20the%20amount%20of%20errors%20quantum%20computers%20generate%20while%20operating.%20Quantum%20computers%20aren't%20your%20standard%20laptop%20or%20desktop%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20your%20laptop%2C%20which%20uses%20bits%20to%20process%20information%2C%20quantum%20computers%20use%20something%20called%20qubits%2C%20short%20for%20quantum%20bits.%20Bits%20are%20binary%20digits%2C%20meaning%20they%20can%20only%20exist%20in%20one%20state%20at%20a%20time%2C%20typically%20as%20a%200%20or%201.%20Qubits%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20exist%20in%20multiple%20states%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20important%20because%20it%20means%20you%20can%20process%20significantly%20more%20information%20at%20much%20faster%20speeds%20with%20qubits.%20That's%20the%20ultimate%20promise%20of%20quantum%20computers%3A%20They%20can%20process%20so%20much%20data%20in%20such%20short%20periods%20that%20they'll%20revolutionize%20science%20and%20medicine%2C%20helping%20us%20solve%20problems%20related%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20health%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20are%20far%20too%20complex%20to%20tackle%20with%20today's%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20right%20now%2C%20the%20best%20quantum%20computers%20can%20perform%20around%20a%20thousand%20operations%20before%20errors%20overwhelm%20the%20processing%20system%2C%20Steve%20Brierley%2C%20quantum%20computing%20researcher%20and%20CEO%20of%20error%20correction%20company%20Riverlane%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20get%20to%20this%20big%20potential%20like%20transformational%20technology%2C%20we%20need%20to%20get%20to%20millions%20and%20trillions%20of%20free%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Brierley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20Google's%20Willow%20chip%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20breakthrough.%20With%20the%20Willow%20chip%2C%20the%20more%20qubits%20Google%20adds%2C%20the%20fewer%20errors%20the%20system%20creates.%20The%20Willow%20chip%20reduces%20errors%20exponentially%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20The%20ability%20to%20reduce%20errors%20while%20scaling%20qubits%20is%20known%20in%20the%20field%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bbelow%20threshold%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20been%20an%20unresolved%20challenge%20since%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20plays%20out%20via%20processing%20speed.%20Google%20said%20its%20researchers%20used%20the%20Random%20Circuit%20Sampling%20benchmark%20to%20compare%20computing%20speeds%20across%20various%20technologies.%20The%20RCS%20is%20a%20standard%20in%20the%20field%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bclassically%20hardest%26quot%3B%20benchmark%20to%20pass%2C%20to%20compare%20computing%20speeds%20across%20various%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20its%20Willow%20chip%20can%20perform%20the%20standard%20benchmark%20computation%20in%20under%20five%20minutes%2C%20which%20would%20take%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20supercomputers%2010%20septillion%20years%20to%20complete%20%E2%80%94%20longer%20than%20the%20known%20age%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20field%20of%20quantum%2C%20error%20correction%20is%20much%20more%20difficult%20and%20requires%20more%20hardware%20to%20function%20properly%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Google's%20advancement%20is%20so%20important%2C%20Mark%20Saffman%2C%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%20and%20director%20at%20the%20Wisconsin%20Quantum%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrierley%20compared%20Google's%20quantum%20computing%20advancement%20to%20what%20mobile%20networks%20experienced%20when%20they%20shifted%20from%201G%20to%202G%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20mobile%20networks%20shifted%20from%201G%20to%202G%2C%20%26quot%3BQualcomm%20added%20error%20correction%20into%20the%20stack%20and%20this%20created%20a%20huge%20uplift%20in%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20Brierley%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20exactly%20what's%20happening%20right%20now%20in%20quantum%20computing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20constantly%20correct%20errors%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bkey%20part%26quot%3B%20of%20building%20a%20quantum%20computer%2C%20he%20said.%20Once%20companies%20are%20able%20to%20scale%20qubits%20and%20advance%20quantum%20computing%20forward%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20point%20of%20real-world%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf7715d1-d6f4-410b-8508-76f726683999%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReal-world%20impact%20is%20likely%20years%20away%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20in%20a%20press%20briefing%20about%20the%20development%20that%20it%20has%20already%20partnered%20with%20companies%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%2C%20material%20science%2C%20and%20battery%20space%2C%20among%20others.%20However%2C%20advancements%20in%20those%20fields%20may%20not%20be%20right%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaffman%20said%20he%20would%20like%20to%20see%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-major-impact-marketing-citi-cmo-alex-craddock-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20real-world%20application%3C%2Fa%3Es%20in%20five%20years%2C%20but%20it's%20difficult%20to%20provide%20an%20exact%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESebastian%20Weidt%2C%20quantum%20computer%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Sussex%20and%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20quantum%20computing%20company%20Universal%20Quantum%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20still%20a%20little%20while%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20quantum%20computing%20impacting%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeidt%20said%20that%20while%20there%20was%20initially%20hope%20that%20intermediate-scale%20computers%20could%20offer%20some%20value%20to%20a%20general%20consumer%2C%20the%20science%20shows%20that%20qubits%20need%20to%20be%20scaled%20by%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20and%20eventually%20millions%20to%20unlock%20real-world%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20major%20roadblocks%20on%20their%20roadmap%20that%20need%20to%20be%20overcome%20for%20that%20technology%20to%20get%20to%20that%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Weidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Google's%20advancement%20moves%20quantum%20computing%20research%20to%20the%20next%20stage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20while%20investors%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20in%20the%20immediate%20short%20term%2C%20Brierley%20said%20announcements%20like%20this%20help%20attract%20capital%20and%20talent%20to%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20still%20very%20very%20far%20to%20go%20to%20make%20it%20useful%20relative%20to%20conventional%20computers%2C%26quot%3B%20Saffman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20a%20great%20step%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-google-quantum-willow-chip-breakthrough-big-deal-researchers-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733955253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6758710891c1cc343d47a6ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-google-quantum-willow-chip-breakthrough-big-deal-researchers-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google's%20Willow%20chip%20reduces%20errors%20exponentially%2C%20addressing%20a%20problem%20the%20industry%20has%20faced%20for%20almost%2030%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A118%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-google-quantum-willow-chip-breakthrough-big-deal-researchers-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Luigi%20Mangione%20had%20spondylolisthesis%2C%20a%20lower%20back%20condition.%20He%20wrote%20about%20painful%20symptoms%20like%20sciatica%20on%20Reddit.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luigi%20Mangione%20led%20from%20the%20Blair%20County%20Courthouse%20after%20an%20extradition%20hearing%20in%20Hollidaysburg%2C%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6759f03f91c1cc343d47eb49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22437%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuigi%20Mangione%20led%20from%20the%20Blair%20County%20Courthouse%20after%20an%20extradition%20hearing%20in%20Hollidaysburg%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Swensen%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELuigi%20Mangione%2C%20charged%20with%20killing%20the%20CEO%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%2C%20had%20a%20lower%20back%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESpondylolisthesis%20occurs%20when%20one%20vertebra%20in%20your%20spine%20slips%20out%20of%20alignment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMangione%20seemingly%20frequented%20a%20subreddit%20for%20the%20condition%20and%20wrote%20about%20symptoms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELuigi%20Mangione%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20man%20charged%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangione-unitedhealth-ceo-killing-person-what-to-know-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekilling%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20suffered%20from%20a%20spinal%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-myth-luigi-mangione-preceded-man-unitedhealthcare-murder-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMangione's%20social%20media%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20included%20several%20references%20to%20back%20pain.%20On%20X%2C%20Mangione's%20banner%20included%20an%20X-ray%20image%20of%20a%20spine%20after%20a%20spinal%20fusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20Reddit%20account%2C%20he%20posted%20in%20a%20subreddit%20for%20spondylolisthesis%2C%20a%20lower%20back%20condition%20most%20often%20caused%20by%20joint%20deterioration.%20Mangione%20also%20mentioned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-luigi-mangione-charged-unitedhealthcare-ceo-murder-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20had%20spondylolisthesis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20handwritten%20notes%20from%202019%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3728d31-1715-4d00-85c4-12928f557c68%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpondylolisthesis%20can%20cause%20pain%20and%20stiffness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20model%20of%20spondylolisthesis.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6759ef5f91c1cc343d47eaf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20model%20of%20spondylolisthesis.%3Cp%3EJitendra%20Jadhav%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Cleveland%20Clinic%2C%20spondylolisthesis%20is%20usually%20caused%20by%20aging%20(as%20the%20discs%20holding%20the%20vertebrae%20weaken)%20or%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20condition%20when%20one%20of%20the%20bones%20in%20the%20spine%20falls%20out%20of%20alignment%20and%20%26quot%3Bpresses%20down%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20vertebra%20below%20it.%20That%20pressure%20on%20nearby%20nerves%20can%20cause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Flow-back-pain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20back%20pain.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20symptoms%20include%20sciatica%20(nerve%20pain%20that%20runs%20down%20from%20the%20lower%20back%20to%20the%20legs)%2C%20back%20stiffness%2C%20numbness%2C%20and%20difficulty%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20needs%20spinal%20fusion%20surgery%20to%20realign%20their%20vertebrae%3B%20depending%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20symptoms%2C%20rest%2C%20physical%20therapy%2C%20and%20wearing%20a%20brace%20can%20help%20reduce%20pain%2C%20as%20can%20taking%20over-the-counter%20medications%20when%20symptoms%20flare%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e11a1a61-37c6-47f1-a427-7e471c6cd1a0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMangione%20had%20sciatica%2C%20a%20common%20symptom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Mangione%20moved%20to%20a%20co-living%20space%20in%20Honolulu%20called%20Surfbreak.%20According%20to%20a%20Reddit%20post%2C%20he%20experienced%20sciatica%2C%20nerve%20pain%20that%20runs%20down%20from%20the%20lower%20back%20to%20the%20legs%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20a%20surf%20session.%20%26quot%3BA%20few%20weeks%20later%20I%20slipped%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20and%20my%20right%20glute%20locked%20and%20right%20leg%20shut%20down%20for%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%202022.%20%26quot%3BCouldn't%20support%20any%20weight%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20his%20back%20surgery%20in%202023%2C%20Mangione%20also%20described%20having%20%26quot%3Bnear-constant%20burning%2Ftwitching%20in%20both%20ankles%2Fcalves%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bback%20and%20genital%20pain%26quot%3B%20on%20Reddit%20%E2%80%94%20symptoms%20of%20sciatica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ER.J.%20Martin%2C%20who%20owns%20Surfbreak%2C%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2024%2F12%2F09%2Fnyregion%2Funitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-news%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20shortly%20after%20moving%20in%2C%20Mangione%20experienced%20such%20debilitating%20pain%20from%20a%20group%20surfing%20lesson%20that%20he%20needed%20Martin%20to%20switch%20out%20his%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20also%20told%20Martin%20that%20his%20condition%20prevented%20him%20from%20being%20in%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knew%20that%20dating%20and%20being%20physically%20intimate%20with%20his%20back%20condition%20wasn't%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20him%20telling%20me%20that%2C%20and%20my%20heart%20just%20breaks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20back%20surgery%20seemed%20to%20improve%20Mangione's%20symptoms%20%E2%80%94%20he%20posted%20in%202023%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuccess.%26quot%3B%20But%20by%20June%202024%2C%20he%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangiones-deleted-social-media-posts-clues-politics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriticizing%20doctors%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20eventually%20lost%20touch%20with%20friends%20and%20family.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mayo%20Clinic%2C%20spinal%20fusion%20surgeries%20for%20spondylolisthesis%20%26quot%3Bcan%20have%20very%20good%20outcomes%20when%20performed%20well%20and%20for%20the%20right%20reasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-spondylolisthesis-luigi-mangione-lower-back-condition-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733955211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6759f02e52dd0818d1a682c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-spondylolisthesis-luigi-mangione-lower-back-condition-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luigi%20Mangione%2C%20who%20was%20charged%20with%20killing%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20had%20a%20lower%20back%20condition%20called%20spondylolisthesis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-spondylolisthesis-luigi-mangione-lower-back-condition-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%2C%20UAE%20Counterpart%20To%20Hold%20Strategic%20Talks%20Today%2C%20Syria%20On%20Agenda%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20will%20look%20to%20further%20their%20already-strong%20strategic%20partnership%20to%20an%20all-time%20high%20when%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20his%20counterpart%20Abdullah%20Bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%20will%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20today%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20and%20Sheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%20will%20review%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20UAE%20and%20focus%20on%20enhancing%20the%20strategic%20partnership.%20The%20meeting%20also%20assumes%20significance%20as%20it%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20regime%20change%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Asia%2C%20popularly%20called%20the%20Middle-East%20by%20Western%20nations%2C%20is%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%2C%20with%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20simmering%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20Syria%20being%20extremely%20volatile%2C%20and%20Turkey%20launching%20strikes%20on%20Syria%20too.%20Bashar%20Al-Assad%20has%20been%20granted%20asylum%20in%20Moscow%20and%20Russia%20has%20lost%20its%20access%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%20with%20the%20Tartus%20naval%20base%20in%20Syria%20now%20no%20longer%20in%20its%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20will%20discuss%20the%20crises%20in%20the%20middle-east%20in%20great%20detail.%20Besides%20geopolitics%2C%20and%20strategic%20ties%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20and%20Sheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%20will%20have%20a%20comprehensive%20dialogue%20on%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20UAE%2C%20including%20trade%20and%20commerce%2C%20investment%2C%20cultural%20and%20scientific%20ties%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20UAE%2C%20will%20then%20call%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20historic%20visit%20to%20the%20UAE%20in%20August%202015%20that%20elevated%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20a%20Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20nations%20also%20signed%20the%20landmark%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20or%20CEPA%20in%202022%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20massive%20upswing%20in%20trade%20and%20investment%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%20The%20trad