r%20job%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20family%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Reasonable%20amount%20for%20legal%20battle%20for%20a%20wife%20who%20is%20not%20working%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20will%20be%20the%20financial%20status%20of%20the%20husband%2C%20his%20earnings%20and%20other%20responsibilities%20along%20with%20alimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20factors%2C%20said%20the%20top%20court%2C%20do%20not%20form%20a%20simple%20formula%20but%20serve%20as%20guidelines%20while%20fixing%20permanent%20alimony%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20permanent%20alimony%20should%20not%20penalize%20the%20husband%20but%20should%20be%20made%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20ensuring%20a%20decent%20standard%20of%20living%20for%20the%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20development%20earlier%20today%2C%20dismissing%20a%20dowry%20case%20against%20a%20man%20and%20his%20parents%2C%20a%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%20observed%20that%20the%20provision%20is%20sometimes%20exploited%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20personal%20vendetta%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20Atul%20Subhash%20has%20reignited%20a%20broader%20debate%20over%20the%20misuse%20of%20dowry%20laws%20in%20India.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20previously%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20misusing%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20which%20addresses%20cruelty%20by%20husbands%20and%20their%20relatives%20against%20married%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%20the%20Bengaluru%20techie%20called%20for%20justice%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BJustice%20is%20Due%26quot%3B%20on%20every%20single%20page%20of%20the%2024-page%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20and%20Nikita%20met%20on%20a%20matchmaking%20website%20and%20married%20in%202019.%20The%20couple%20became%20parents%20to%20a%20boy%20the%20following%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife's%20family%20would%20repeatedly%20demand%20money%20running%20into%20several%20lakhs.%20When%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20more%20money%2C%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20home%20with%20their%20son%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20first%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case%2C%20but%20later%20hiked%20this%20to%20Rs%203%20crore.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733944260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fcbjhjd3o_supreme-court-of-india_625x300_11_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-techie-atul-subhashs-suicide-supreme-court-lays-down-8-factors-for-deciding-alimony-7227170%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20laid%20down%20an%20eight-point%20formula%20for%20deciding%20alimony%20amount%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20surrounding%20the%20suicide%20of%20Bengaluru-based%20techie%20Atul%20Subhash%2C%20who%20had%20alleged%20harassment%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20in-laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-techie-atul-subhashs-suicide-supreme-court-lays-down-8-factors-for-deciding-alimony-7227170%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLike%20Beast...%26quot%3B%3A%20What%20Techie's%20Wife%20Claimed%2C%20What%20He%20Said%20In%20Suicide%20Note%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20outcry%20over%20Bengaluru%20techie%20Atul%20Subhash's%20death%20by%20suicide%20over%20alleged%20harassment%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20details%20have%20emerged%20of%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20her%20in%202022%2C%20alleging%20harassment%20and%20assault%20for%20dowry.%20Ms%20Singhania%20has%20alleged%20that%20he%20treated%20the%20husband-wife%20relationship%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20beast%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20family's%20demand%20for%20dowry%20contributed%20to%20her%20father%20suffering%20a%20stroke%20and%20dying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%2024-page%20suicide%20note%2C%20however%2C%20Subhash%20has%20replied%20to%20nearly%20every%20allegation%20made%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singhania%20filed%20the%20complaint%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jaunpur%20-%20where%20her%20family%20lives%20-%20in%20April%202022%20claiming%20she%20was%20harassed%20and%20assaulted%20for%20dowry.%20Subhash%2C%20his%20brother%20and%20their%20parents%20were%20named%20as%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Dowry%20Prohibition%20Act%2C%201961%2C%20the%20complaint%20also%20had%20charges%20like%20cruelty%20by%20husband%20or%20relatives%2C%20assault%2C%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20Nikita%20said%20she%20got%20married%20to%20Subhash%20on%20April%2026%2C%202019%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20and%20in-laws%20were%20dissatisfied%20with%20what%20her%20parents%20gave%20them%20during%20the%20wedding%20and%20demanded%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(They)%20started%20torturing%20me%20physically%20and%20mentally%20for%20dowry.%20When%20I%20told%20my%20parents%20about%20the%20harassment%20and%20dowry%2C%20my%20parents%20explained%20to%20me%20that%20everything%20will%20be%20fine%2C%20listen%20and%20keep%20living%20with%20it.%20But%20no%20improvement%20of%20any%20kind%20came%20in%20my%20husband%20and%20in-laws%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20according%20to%20the%20PTI%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20husband%20started%20to%20beat%20me%20up%20after%20drinking%20alcohol%20and%20started%20treating%20the%20husband-wife%20relationship%20with%20me%20like%20a%20beast.%20He%20used%20to%20transfer%20my%20entire%20salary%20from%20my%20account%20to%20his%20account%20by%20threatening%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%20however%2C%20Subhash%20states%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Ms%20Singhania%2C%20he%20earned%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20a%20year%20as%20an%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20professional%20when%20she%20left%20the%20house%20in%202021%20and%20Rs%2080%20lakh%20after%20that.%20He%20said%20her%20claim%20of%20his%20family%20asking%20for%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20was%20%26quot%3Blaughable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20demanded%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20dowry%20is%20the%20most%20laughable%20allegation.%20My%20wife%20has%20claimed%20that%20I%20had%20a%20CTC%20of%20Rs%2040%20lakhs%20when%20she%20left%20the%20house.%20My%20wife%20also%20claimed%20that%20I%20have%20a%20CTC%20of%20Rs%2080%20Lakhs%20later%20in%20the%20case.%20Why%20would%20a%20man%20making%20Rs%2040%20or%2080%20lakhs%20would%20ever%20demand%20Rs%2010%20lakhs%20and%20leave%20his%20wife%20and%20child%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20allegation%20of%20him%20beating%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20techie%20said%20she%20had%20never%20produced%20any%20evidence%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20beat%20her%20up%20black%20and%20blue%20after%20getting%20drunk.%20A%20well%20built%20man%20like%20me%2C%20if%20decides%20to%20beat%20someone%20black%20and%20blue%20(sic)%2C%20would%20leave%20a%20person%20with%20broken%20bones%2C%20bleeding%20and%20at%20least%20some%20marks.%20Why%20did%20she%20not%20produce%20any%20photo%20of%20it%20or%20anyone%20who%20is%20a%20witness%20(%20we%20often%20had%20a%20house%20maid%2C%20cook%20etc)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFather's%20Death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%2C%20Ms%20Singhania%20also%20claimed%20that%2C%20irritated%20by%20the%20words%20of%20her%20in-laws%20and%20because%20of%20their%20demand%20for%20d