-business-4-1733830341-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388206%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202007%2C%20Jagpal%20quit%20teaching%20to%20devote%20himself%20fully%20to%20beekeeping.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20an%20agricultural%20background%2C%20where%20earning%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20acre%20from%20wheat%20farming%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20Jagpal%20realised%20that%20beekeeping%20offered%20far%20greater%20advantages%20over%20traditional%20farming%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeekeeping%20requires%20a%20one-time%20investment%20and%20provides%20yields%20year%20after%20year%2C%20unlike%20farming%2C%20where%20you%20have%20to%20re-sow%20for%20every%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jagpal%20(59)%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20a%20big%20difference.%20Plus%2C%20any%20small%20farmer%20can%20start%20beekeeping%2C%20even%20without%20much%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Jagpal%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20advantages%20of%20beekeeping%2C%20its%20impact%20on%20local%20farmers%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20wider%20adoption%20of%20this%20eco-friendly%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20classroom%20to%20apiary%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagpal%20began%20his%20career%20as%20an%20English%20teacher%20at%20a%20private%20secondary%20school.%20However%2C%20a%20chance%20encounter%20with%20beekeeping%20through%20a%20relative%20sparked%20a%20newfound%20passion.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20c