betapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20a%20red-light%20district%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseema%E2%80%99s%20home%20was%20Chaturbhuj%20Sthan%2C%20a%20red-light%20district%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar.%20Named%20after%20a%20Vishnu%20temple%2C%20the%20area%20has%20historically%20been%20home%20to%20sex%20workers%20and%20%3Cem%3Etawaifs%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20its%20religious%20name%20does%20not%20shield%20the%20community%20from%20societal%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20not%20tell%20people%20who%20I%20am%20and%20where%20I%20come%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20remembers%20asking%20her%20father%2C%20who%20quickly%20shut%20her%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20girls%20from%20school%20would%20all%20walk%20home%20together%2C%20but%20they%20would%20take%20a%20long%20wounded%20route%20to%20avoid%20my%20%3Cem%3Egully%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20were%20told%20to%2C%20so%20I%E2%80%99d%20go%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Naseema%20was%20a%20witness%20to%20frequent%20police%20raids%20in%20her%20neighbourhood.%20These%20experiences%20left%20a%20lasting%20impact%2C%20and%20it%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20she%20began%20to%20fully%20understand%20the%20marginalisation%20her%20community%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ima